<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>112</hymn_number>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A kan Khamhtu Bawi Bethlehem khua ah, Caw rawleinak kuang chungah a
 hrin cang. Maw khuaruahharnak ngaingai a si ko, Keimah kha kawl duh ah.

[C1]
   Keimah kha a ka kawl, (ka kawl ka kawl) Keimah kha a ka kawl, Maw
   lunglawmhnak kha khuaruahharnak in, Keimah a ka kawl ko.

[V2]
 Maw Bawi Jesuh nih vailamtahnak ah, Ka sualnak caah thihnak a in cang,
 Maw zeitluk in dah khuaruahhar a si, Keimah ca'h a thi cang.

[C2]
   Keimah kha a ka kawl, (ka kawl ka kawl) Keimah kha a ka kawl, Maw
   lunglawmhnak kha khuaruahharnak in, Keimah a ka kawl ko.

[V3]
 Bawi Jesuh nih a zungzal vawlei mi, Lam palh sualmi tuu vialte kha a
 kawl, A saupi duhsah te in a ka auh, Keimah kha a ka auh.

[C3]
   Keimah kha a ka kawl, (ka kawl ka kawl) Keimah kha a ka kawl, Maw
   lunglawmhnak kha khuaruahharnak in, Keimah a ka kawl ko.

[V4]
 Jesuh vawlei ah a rung tum than lai, Kum saupi si hmanhseh hi bia a
 hmun, Vancung in a rung tum lio ka hmuh lai, A tum lai keimah ca.

[C4]
   Keimah kha a ka kawl, (ka kawl ka kawl) Keimah kha a ka kawl, Maw
   lunglawmhnak kha khuaruahharnak in, Keimah a ka kawl ko.</lyrics>
<title>KEIMAH KHA A KA KAWL CH112</title>
</song>